As we looked earlier in 1 Corinthians chapter 16,

00:41:07.440 --> 00:41:12.440
we find that Paul originally said, if the Lord permit.

00:41:12.820 --> 00:41:17.040
I believe that those few words, those four simple words,

00:41:17.040 --> 00:41:19.840
if the Lord permit, that that should have helped

00:41:19.840 --> 00:41:22.660
to prevent a misunderstanding.

00:41:23.660 --> 00:41:27.180
But you know, as much as you might try to do

00:41:27.180 --> 00:41:29.260
to prevent a misunderstanding, you can't keep

00:41:29.260 --> 00:41:31.560
