00:42:32.080 --> 00:42:34.000
Examine yourself.

00:42:34.000 --> 00:42:36.160
Take that step back.

00:42:36.160 --> 00:42:38.600
Helps to diffuse the whole situation anyway.

00:42:39.440 --> 00:42:41.920
